Hurry up.

05:44.578 --> 05:46.647
Did you get that review
I put on your desk?

05:46.680 --> 05:48.081
Yes, I got it, thank you.

05:48.115 --> 05:49.817
I loved seeing
that guy eat crow

05:49.850 --> 05:51.852
after what he said
about you in Doll's House.

05:51.885 --> 05:54.021
Don't you take my reviews
a little too personally?

05:54.054 --> 05:55.523
No, I don't think so.

05:55.556 --> 05:57.024
Every time
we're in a restaurant

05:57.057 --> 05:58.559
and you see a critic,

05:58.592 --> 06:00.360
you want to throw
your butter knife at him.

06:00.394 --> 06:02.430
I would've got the last guy
if he hadn't moved.

06:02.463 --> 06:04.598
Oh, you missed a spot.

06:21.815 --> 06:24.117
Hello, lovely ladies.

06:24.151 --> 06:25.719
Hello. Here's
your breakfast, Michael.

06:25.753 --> 06:27.888
Thanks. Toast is done.

06:27.921 --> 06:29.557
[gasp] Damn!

06:30.924 --> 06:33.594
Jerry, I know
what I'm talking about.

06:33.627 --> 06:35.429
